Bell Canada Enterprises Inc said itextended to June 30 from June 4 a short-term voluntary saleprogram for shareholders owning 10 or fewer Bell Canada commonshares.    The plan allows such shareholders of record at April 21 tosell their shares at market price without incurring brokeragecommissions or other charges.    Bell Canada was quoted at 42 dlrs, up 1/4, in afternoontrading on the Toronto Stock Exchange. Reuter&#3;